===================
 PyBlosxom Release
===================

1. Update the version number and date in:
   * setup.py 
   * Pyblosxom/pyblosxom.py
   * docs/conf.py

2. Commit the changes

3. Tag the commit::

      git tag -a pyblosxom_x_y

4. Build the tarball::

      git archive \
          --format=tar \
          --prefix=pyblosxom-x.y/ $TAG > pyblosxom-x.y.tar

   This builds the tarball.

5. Build the docs::

      cd docs/
      make html

6. Push the docs and the new tarball to the web-site.

7. Update PYPI::

      python setup.py register
